@startuml SD07_Comment_Notification
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
title SD-07: Create Comment + Real-Time Notification

actor "Author" as A
actor "Commenter" as U
participant "Astro\nFrontend" as FE
participant "Envoy\nGateway" as GW
participant "Comment\nService" as CMT
database "ScyllaDB" as SCYLLA
queue "Kafka" as KAFKA
participant "Notification\nService" as NOTIF
database "Redis\n(db3)" as REDIS
database "pg-platform" as DB

U -> FE : Write reply on Author's post
FE -> GW : POST /api/comments\n{post_id, parent_id, body}\n+ JWT
GW -> GW : Validate JWT + rate limit

GW -> CMT : gRPC CreateComment()
CMT -> CMT : Build materialized path\n(parent_path + "/" + new_id)
CMT -> SCYLLA : INSERT comment\n(partition: post_id,\nclustering: path)
CMT --> GW : 201 Created {comment_id}
GW --> FE : JSON response
FE --> U : Comment appears in thread

== Async: Notification ==
CMT ->> KAFKA : Publish "CommentCreated"\n{post_id, parent_id,\nauthor_id, commenter}

KAFKA ->> NOTIF : Consume event
NOTIF -> NOTIF : Identify recipients:\n- post author\n- parent comment author

NOTIF -> REDIS : Lookup user_id -> pod_id\n(WebSocket registry)
alt Author is ONLINE
    NOTIF -> REDIS : INCR unread:author_id
    NOTIF -> A : Push via WebSocket\n"New reply on your post"
else Author is OFFLINE
    NOTIF -> DB : Store notification\n(status: unread)
    note right of DB
        Delivered when Author
        reconnects WebSocket
    end note
end
@enduml
